952
01:26:17,580 --> 01:26:18,410
ya, bukan?

953
01:26:23,120 --> 01:26:24,910
Kenapa kau mentertawakanku?

954
01:26:26,660 --> 01:26:28,620
Aku sudah berbaik hati!

955
01:26:28,750 --> 01:26:33,410
Aku telah memberimu kesempatan
untuk menebus kesalahanmu!

956
01:26:33,830 --> 01:26:34,950
Sekarang tanda tangani!

957
01:26:35,040 --> 01:26:36,620
- Elizabeth, tolong.
- Aku berdoa.

958
01:26:37,080 --> 01:26:39,750
Pegang pena bulunya.
Sekarang tanda tangani.

959
01:26:41,120 --> 01:26:42,410
- Tanda tangani.
- Ayo.

960
01:26:47,370 --> 01:26:48,290
Aku tidak bisa.

961
01:26:57,450 --> 01:26:58,290
Penjaga.

962
01:26:58,370 --> 01:27:00,870
- Tidak. Paduka.
- Elizabeth...

963
01:27:01,160 --> 01:27:04,120
- Tidak!
- Tidak!

964
01:27:05,700 --> 01:27:07,120
- Hentikan!
- Tidak!

965
01:27:08,580 --> 01:27:09,410
Turunkan dia.

966
01:27:09,500 --> 01:27:11,250
Kumohon, jangan!

967
01:27:12,910 --> 01:27:14,330
Kumohon, tunggu!

968
01:27:59,750 --> 01:28:01,500
Saatnya melakukan serangan terbuka.

969
