dan lima puluh tentara.

985
01:29:40,870 --> 01:29:41,750
Majulah.

986
01:29:45,330 --> 01:29:46,450
Tidak apa-apa.

987
01:30:01,370 --> 01:30:02,450
Raja!

988
01:30:02,750 --> 01:30:04,120
Berhenti!

989
01:30:08,790 --> 01:30:13,250
Jika aku mati, kau harus merebus tubuhku
dan membawa tulangku

990
