Clifford!

1110
01:43:20,160 --> 01:43:21,830
Kau tahu siapa aku?

1111
01:43:26,870 --> 01:43:29,200
Siapa namaku?

1112
01:43:30,000 --> 01:43:30,950
Douglas.

1113
01:43:31,200 --> 01:43:32,500
Ya!

1114
01:43:45,200 --> 01:43:46,040
Tembak!

1115
01:43:49,000 --> 01:43:50,200
Bruce!

1116
01:43:50,290 --> 01:43:51,160
Kau berengsek!

1117
01:43:57,040 --> 01:43:59,790
Serang!

1118
01:44:03,040 --> 01:44:04,250
Cari Bruce!

1119
01:44:07,330 --> 01:44:09,450
Putari rawanya!

1120
01:44:10,950 --> 01:44:12,080
Mereka terjebak!

1121
01:44:12,910 --> 01:44:14,200
Pertahankan formasi!

1122
